<body lang=3D"EN-NZ" link=3D"blue" vlink=3D"purple" style=3D"word-wrap:brea=
k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Dear Raff=
aella,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Thank you=
 for reaching out and sharing your concerns about the outcome of your priva=
cy request. We understand this process is important to you and appreciate t=
he opportunity to assist further.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">In respon=
se to your previous request, Tower provided all the personal information we=
 hold on record. This included:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul style=3D"margin-top:0cm" type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"ms=
o-fareast-language:EN-US">A comprehensive IT search using the prompts and v=
ariations you specified<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=
=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Sha=
reFile logs<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list=
:l4 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">The NotifyUs re=
port from the Office of the Privacy Commissioner<o:p></o:p></span></li><li =
class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"mso-fa=
reast-language:EN-US">Explanations for any redactions<o:p></o:p></span></li=
><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"m=
so-fareast-language:EN-US">All relevant correspondence (internal and extern=
al)<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:36.0pt"><span style=3D"mso-fare=
ast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Below is =
the screenshot from your request made:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<table class=3D"MsoNormalTable" border=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" cellpadding=
=3D"0" style=3D"border-collapse:collapse">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td width=3D"623" valign=3D"top" style=3D"width:467.5pt;border:solid window=
text 1.5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><img widt=
h=3D"1125" height=3D"407" style=3D"width:11.7187in;height:4.2395in" id=3D"P=
icture_x0020_1" src=3D"cid:image003.png@01DC5F95.2639A4B0"></span><span sty=
le=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">On 1 July=
 2025, you requested a full copy of your claim files, which we provided. Pl=
ease note that correspondence does not necessary form part of claim files, =
and at that time we did not include
 a full IT database search for communications. We have now completed a full=
 system search for claim C90306256 and uploaded the additional corresponden=
ce to your folder, which you can access here</span>:
<a href=3D"https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sf8d9e0854e8947a3b0e4c249d82c2b0=
1">https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sf8d9e0854e8947a3b0e4c249d82c2b01</a><o:=
p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Based on our searches, we believe we do not hold any=
 further information containing the wording =E2=80=9C23 Mays,=E2=80=9D =E2=
=80=9C23 Mays Road,=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CC90306048,=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CC9030625=
6,=E2=80=9D or any name variations in our systems.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Under Inf=
ormation Privacy Principle 6 of the Privacy Act 2020, we are required to pr=
ovide access to personal information we hold. This obligation includes ensu=
ring the information is meaningful and
 that providing it does not become unreasonable. Based on the steps taken, =
we believe the specific information you are seeking either does not exist o=
r cannot be located despite reasonable efforts.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">That said=
, we would still like to help where possible. If you could clarify or narro=
w down the exact details you are looking for, we will do our best to check =
again within the content already provided.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">If you re=
main unsatisfied with our response, you have the option to lodge a formal c=
omplaint with the Office of the Privacy Commissioner.
<a href=3D"https://www.privacy.org.nz/your-rights/making-a-complaint-to-the=
-privacy-commissioner/complaint-landing-page/?SecurityID=3D4263e8575b7718fb=
1f5bf0015055638884935eee">
Office of the Privacy Commissioner | Submit a complaint</a><o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Thank you=
 for your understanding, and please let us know if you=E2=80=99d like to re=
fine your request so we can assist further.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Warm rega=
rds,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<table class=3D"MsoNormalTable" border=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" cellpadding=
=3D"0" width=3D"599" style=3D"width:449.25pt;border-collapse:collapse">
<tbody>
<tr style=3D"height:97.5pt">
<td width=3D"191" colspan=3D"2" style=3D"width:143.25pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0=
cm 5.4pt;height:97.5pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><img bord=
er=3D"0" width=3D"175" height=3D"123" style=3D"width:1.8229in;height:1.2812=
in" id=3D"Picture_x0020_112374268" src=3D"cid:image001.png@01DC5F8C.180AE6A=
0"></span><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ligat=
ures:standardcontextual;mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</td>
<td width=3D"408" colspan=3D"2" style=3D"width:306.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0c=
m 5.4pt;height:97.5pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"line-height:150%"><b><span style=3D"font-si=
ze:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#=
002060;mso-ligatures:standardcontextual;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Privacy=
